        "reason": "Aggressive Growth was the only strategy to convert pipeline activity into a quote (1 quote) while also generating the highest lead volume (13). With zero revenue across all strategies in this simulation window, quote generation is the most meaningful leading indicator of future revenue, giving Aggressive Growth a decisive edge."
